header.gameNote: LAS VEGAS BOWL PRESENTED BY GEICO

videos.description: Houston QB Greg Ward Jr. caps off a 10-play, 74-yard drive with a two-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Ward's TD run gives Houston lead

videos.description: San Diego State head coach Rocky Long wants team to keep running ball like it did in second quarter
videos.headline: San Diego State head coach Rocky Long wants team to keep running ball like it did in second quarter

videos.description: Greg Ward Jr. pass intercepted, Kameron Kelly return for no gain to the Houst 36
videos.headline: G. Ward Jr. pass intercepted by K. Kelly

videos.description: Greg Ward Jr. pass intercepted by Calvin Munson, return for 12 yds to the SDSt 32
videos.headline: Ward Jr. throws his second pick of game

videos.description: Christian Chapman pass complete to Donnel Pumphrey for 26 yds to the Houst 32 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Pumphrey shows off his hands

videos.description: Donnel Pumphrey is chasing the all-time rushing record, and in the process busts through the line to go 32 yards into the end zone to give San Diego State its first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Pumphrey busts through for 32-yard TD

videos.description: Ron Smith slips between the blocks and picks off the quick out pass from Greg Ward Jr., going 54 yards the other way to the house putting San Diego State up 20-10.
videos.headline: Smith jumps the route for SDSU pick-six

videos.description: In the fourth quarter, San Diego State's Donnel Pumphrey takes the toss right and goes 15 yards to pass Ron Dayne for the all-time rushing record in FBS history.
videos.headline: Pumphrey claims the all-time FBS rushing record

videos.description: Curtis Anderson III 28 Yd pass from Christian Chapman for TD
videos.headline: Chapman finds Anderson to extend SDSU lead

videos.description: Juwan Washington run for 7 yds for a TD
videos.headline: J. Washington run for 7 yds for a TD

videos.description: Donnel Pumphrey discusses his emotions after breaking Ron Dayne's FBS rushing record during San Diego State's victory over Houston in the Las Vegas Bowl and is surprised by his father on the field mid-interview.
videos.headline: Pumphrey glad to break the FBS rushing record in his hometown

videos.description: Trophy presentation for San Diego State's Las Vegas Bowl victory
videos.headline: Trophy presentation for San Diego State's Las Vegas Bowl victory

videos.description: San Diego State's Donnel Pumphrey breaks the NCAA career rushing record, running for 115 yards and a touchdown in SDSU's 34-10 rout of Houston.
videos.headline: Pumphrey makes NCAA history in SDSU's Las Vegas Bowl win
